    <span class="page-eyebrow">Nalu Snack Bar</span>
    <h1 class="page-title">Eat Well.<br><em>Stay Fueled.</em></h1>
    <p class="page-sub">All-day dining, cold drinks, and a bar menu. Filipino comfort food with the Pacific outside. Open to guests and walk-ins.</p>
  </div>
</div>

